{
  "name": "Medical Bill Dispute Analyzer",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## \ud83c\udfe5 Medical Bill Dispute Analyzer\n\n### What this workflow does\n1. Watches Google Drive for new medical bills or EOB documents\n2. Extracts all charges, procedure codes, and insurance payments\n3. AI checks for duplicate charges, unbundling, and billing errors\n4. Pauses for human review before flagging the insurer\n5. Logs all disputes to Google Sheets\n6. Sends Slack alert with dispute summary and next steps\n\n### Setup steps\n1. Get PDF Vector API key from pdfvector.com/api-keys\n2. Create Google Drive folder for medical bills\n3. Create Google Sheet with columns:\n   Patient | Provider | Bill Date | Total Charged | Insurance Paid | Patient Owed | Errors Found | Dispute Amount | Status | Processed Date\n4. Update YOUR_FOLDER_ID in New Medical Bill node\n5. Update YOUR_SPREADSHEET_ID and YOUR_SLACK_CHANNEL_ID\n\n### Perfect for\n- Patients reviewing hospital bills\n- Medical billing advocates\n- Insurance claims processors",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "09193be4-603e-4121-af05-1dfb4dd688e6",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        2128,
        -80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "pollTimes": {
          "item": [
